# Google OAuth Credentials (used for Gmail service)
# (Go to https://console.developers.google.com/apis/credentials to create your OAuth credentials)
# Create a new project if you don't have one already
# -> Credentials -> Create credentials -> OAuth Client ID -> Select "Web application"
# For the Authorized JavaScript origins, use: http://localhost:3000
# For the Authorized redirect URIs, use:
#   - http://localhost:8080/api/v1/service-connections/callback/gmail
# Don't forget to enable Gmail API for your project:
#   - Go to https://console.developers.google.com/apis/library
#   - Search for "Gmail API" and click "Enable"
GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=your-google-client-id.apps.googleusercontent.com
GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET=your-google-client-secret

